# Themed Scrollbar

**MANDATORY**: All scrollable areas in the site must use the themed purple scrollbar.

## Implementation

The themed scrollbar is applied **globally** in `frontend/src/index.css`:
- Uses `--primary` (purple) for thumb and `--primary-hover` for hover
- Thin scrollbar (6px)
- Transparent track
- Rounded thumb

## Rule

- Do NOT add custom scrollbar styles that override the global theme
- Do NOT use `scrollbar-gutter` or other scrollbar utilities that conflict
- All `overflow-y-auto` and `overflow-x-auto` elements automatically get the themed scrollbar
- No additional classes needed when adding new scrollable areas
